                    <span>Bhante Henepola Gunaratana gave some pretty easy advice here for the practitioners on how to make The Noble 8 Fold Path as part of their daily life. The book has some very good instruction, however tends to drag with some worthless knowledge here and there. It's very good for the basic practitioner who needs some understanding on how to make the path part of their lives.</span>
                  
              
